<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><style>table, th, td {  border: 1px solid black;}</style><head>    <meta charset="UTF-8" http-equiv="refresh" content="{{.RefreshRate}}" />    <title>Sunscreen homepage</title></head><body><h1>Sunscreen homepage</h1><p>Last updated: {{.Time}} <br> <i>(updates every {{.RefreshRate}} seconds automatically)</i></p><table border="1px solid black">	<tr>		<td><b>Mode:</b></td>		<td>{{.Mode}}</td>	</tr>	<tr>		<td><b>Current position:</b></td>		<td>{{.Position}}</td>	</tr>	<tr>		<td><b>Current light:</b></td>		<td>5</td>	</tr></table><h2>Change sunscreen position</h2><p>Click on one of the below set sunscreen to automatic mode, move it manually up or down.</p><table>	<tr>		<td><a href="/mode/auto">Auto</a></td>		<td>The sunscreen will automatically move up or down, baesed on the light and current time</td>	</tr>	<tr>		<td><a href="/mode/manual/up">Up</a></td>		<td>If sunscreen is not yet up, the suncreen will move up.</td>	</tr>	<tr>		<td><a href="/mode/manual/down">Down</a></td>		<td>If sunscreen is not yet down, the suncreen will move down</td>	</tr></table><p><a href="config">Click here to change the variables</a></p><p><a href="/">Click here to refresh</a></p></body></html>